%F A025993 a(n) = -8*2^n/105+125*5^n/24-343*7^n/20+729*9^n/56. - _R. J. Mathar_, Jun 20 2013
%F A025993 a(n) = 23*a(n-1)-185*a(n-2)+601*a(n-3)-630*a(n-4), with a(0)=1, a(1)=23, a(2)=344, a(3)=4258. - _Harvey P. Dale_, Jul 04 2013
%F A025993 a(n) = (5^(n+1) - 2^(n+1))/3 + 16*a(n-1) - 63*a(n-2). - _Vincenzo Librandi_, Jul 09 2026
%t A025993 CoefficientList[Series[1/((1-2x)(1-5x)(1-7x)(1-9x)),{x,0,30}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Jul 04 2013 *)
